      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jonathan Warkentin</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:162px;\"><a href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/jonathanwarkentinlogiccrazy/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/a/ac/LogicCrazy.jpg\" width=\"160\" height=\"164\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:LogicCrazy.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Logic Crazy <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Jonathan Warkentin</b>, (Logic Crazy)<br />\na Canadian programmer who has been fascinated with the challenge of not only writing chess engines, \nbut also helping others achieve the same feat. He provides tutorials ranging from simplistic engines to advanced engines in video series format. \nHis tutorials demonstrate and explain every step necessary to creating the engine at hand. \nCheck out his videos on his <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Channel <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Video_Tutorials\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Video Tutorials</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Warkentin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/jonathanwarkentinlogiccrazy/\">Jonathan Warkentin Website: LogicCrazy</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://orionchessengine.blogspot.com/\">Orion Chess Engine - Blogger</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Video_Tutorials\">Video Tutorials</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Warkentin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Video Tutorials\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLQV5mozTHmaffB0rBsD6m9VN1azgo5wXl\">Simple Java Chess Engine Tutorial Series</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLQV5mozTHmacMeRzJCW_8K3qw2miYqd0c\">Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial Series</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/V_2-LOvr5E8\">Introduction to an Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial Series</a></dd></dl>\n<ol><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/a5IGltn95Bk\">Bitboards (The Concept of) - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 1</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/cy3xhKk1-ns\">Generating Bitboards - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 2</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/21HYZ8JcOSA\">Chess960 and Favorite Links - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/2XgpJp2LDdM\">Bitwise Operations - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 4</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/General_Setwise_Operations\" title=\"General Setwise Operations\">General Setwise Operations</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/lVt8WREHirk\">Pawn Moves &amp; Optimization (Part 1) - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 5</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn\" title=\"Pawn\">Pawn</a>, <a href=\"/Optimization\" title=\"Optimization\">Optimization</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/YHeV9sfLCro\">Pawn Moves &amp; Optimization (Part 2) - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 6</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/q0wt3m2btlQ\">En Passants - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 7</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/En_passant\" title=\"En passant\">En passant</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/bCH4YK6oq8M\">Sliding Pieces (Part 1) - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 8</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Hyperbola_Quintessence\" title=\"Hyperbola Quintessence\">Hyperbola Quintessence</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/1OG-YVm7aHI\">Sliding Pieces (Part 2) - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 9</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/EiJrEm9aNkQ\">Sliding Pieces (Part 3) - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 10</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/EVJptiAqFSQ\">Knight Moves - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 11</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Knight_Pattern\" title=\"Knight Pattern\">Knight Pattern</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/BOgCppJco2I\">King Movement &amp; Safety - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 12</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/King\" title=\"King\">King</a>, <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/rydv2Si5Lt0\">Black &amp; White Moves - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 13</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/a9-FxSx8yUY\">Castling - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 14</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Castling\" title=\"Castling\">Castling</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/A0HJbwRwILk\">Perft Debugging - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 15</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/DgsVSZZjIko\">Make &amp; Undo Moves - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 16</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Make_Move\" title=\"Make Move\">Make Move</a>, <a href=\"/Unmake_Move\" title=\"Unmake Move\">Unmake Move</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/B9AEQphRkg8\">Perft Algorithm - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 17</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/lARzBG-OuW8\">Importing FEN Strings - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 18</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Forsyth-Edwards_Notation\" title=\"Forsyth-Edwards Notation\">Forsyth-Edwards Notation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/DNvK3lhb6ag\">Divided Perft Routine - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 19</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/bAONObdxF54\">Perft Debugging Example - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 20</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/BIzAfg5sdqg\">Perft Speed &amp; Debugging Tips - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 21</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft_Results\" title=\"Perft Results\">Perft Results</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/vuvTFNreykk\">Universal Chess Interface - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 22</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/D4DBE4UQoAY\">Implementing the UCI - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 23</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/9BrV87doCAM\">UCI Moves (Part 2) - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 24</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/p1YoD30--AM\">UCI Move &amp; Go (Part 3) - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 25</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/ghn0RLx2jLs\">How to Connect the Chess Engine to Arena or any other GUI - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 26</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a>, <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/1YdBLgmoV_E\">Principal Variation Search - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 27</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/2Go0IPVoTtY\">The PVS Algorithm - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 28</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/4FixQ-laeLQ\">The Zero/Null Window Search - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 29</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/QYNRvMolN20\">Transposition Tables &amp; Zobrist Keys - Advanced Java Chess Engine Tutorial 30</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>, <a href=\"/Zobrist_Hashing\" title=\"Zobrist Hashing\">Zobrist Hashing</a></li></ol>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Warkentin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/jonathanwarkentinlogiccrazy/\">Jonathan Warkentin Website: LogicCrazy</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmMjMHTeUEBJJZhxix-N-yg\">Logic Crazy Chess</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301115425\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.016 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 43/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 98/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7420-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301115425 and revision id 21169\n -->\n"
